headline: Robinhood Markets, Inc. Reports May 2025 Operating Data
summary: MENLO PARK, Calif., June 11, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Robinhood Markets, Inc. (“Robinhood”) (NASDAQ: HOOD) today reported select monthly operating data for May 2025. Funded Customers at the end of May were 25.9 million (up about 5 thousand from April 2025, up 1.8 million year-over-year).
